Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with interest point detectors and their evaluation on a dataset of street-level views. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper mentions the application of interest point detectors in autonomous driving. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper compares hand-crafted and deep-learning based interest point detectors. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper deals with the development and evaluation of algorithms for computer vision tasks. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a possible category as the paper mentions the use of deep learning based interest point detectors.
